New Delhi
Dec 10, 2014
Molestation
Description:
			A 22-year-man was today arrested for allegedly misbehaving with a woman in a Haryana Roadways bus at Kashmere Gate in North Delhi here this evening.

"The man, identified as Rajkumar was heavily drunk. He fell on two-three people in that condition, one of whom was a woman. The woman made a PCR call following which our teams rushed to the spot," said a police official.

Police found the man heavily drunk.

The woman said that she doesn't want to press any charges but the man was arrested under preventive sections.

